      "id": "story-001",
      "type": "pasted",
      "title": "Opening Cinematic Script",
      "content": "## ECHOES OF THE VOID - Opening Cinematic\n\n**FADE IN:**\n\n*A vast expanse of stars. Peaceful. Eternal.*\n\n**NARRATOR (V.O.)**\nBefore there was memory, there was the Void.\n\n*The stars begin to flicker, one by one.*\n\n**NARRATOR (V.O.)**\nNot emptiness. Not darkness. Something older. Something hungry.\n\n*A great rift tears across the cosmos. Purple-black tendrils reach outward.*\n\n**NARRATOR (V.O.)**\nWhen the Void came, civilizations fell in silence. Billions of souls... consumed. Their memories scattered like ashes in a cosmic wind.\n\n*We see fragments floating in the void - faces, places, moments frozen in crystal shards.*\n\n**NARRATOR (V.O.)**\nBut memories are stubborn things. They refuse to die. They gather. They wait.\n\n*The fragments begin to coalesce, forming a humanoid shape.*\n\n**NARRATOR (V.O.)**\nThey wait for someone brave enough - or desperate enough - to wield them.\n\n*The figure opens its eyes. They glow with inner light.*\n\n**NARRATOR (V.O.)**\nThey wait for you, Seeker.\n\n*TITLE CARD: ECHOES OF THE VOID*\n\n**FADE TO BLACK.**\n\n---\n\n**Duration:** ~45 seconds\n**Art notes:** Painterly 2D animation, minimal movement, emphasis on atmosphere\n**Music:** Haunting choir, building to crescendo at title",
